If you would encounter any problems with UI, here is REST description

================================================================================

#1 [http://localhost:8080/rest/krapoint/path/submit] [POST]

----This will create new path----

{
    "pointA":"a1",
    "pointB":"a2",
    "estimate": 42
}

Possible errors: not all parameters are present

----This will update new path if it already exists----

{
    "pointA":"a1",
    "pointB":"a2",
    "estimate": 24
}

Possible errors: not all parameters are present

----This will get time of the shortest path between tow points that are connected----

{
    "pointA":"a1",
    "pointB":"a2",
    "calculate": true
}

Possible errors: not all parameters are present, points are not connected

================================================================================

#2 [http://localhost:8080/rest/krapoint/path/delete] [POST]

----This will delete the path----

{
    "pointA":"a1",
    "pointB":"a2"
}

Possible errors: there is no such path

================================================================================
